hn, Kalamazoo, MI.[7] Agencia Espaola de Medicamentos y Productos Sanitarios Healthcare "Centro de informacin online de medicamentos de la AEMPS - CIMA. Available from: URL: https://cima.aemps.es/cima/publico/home.html." ([2018]):[8] "Product Information. Ifex (ifosfamide)." Bristol-Myers Squibb, Princeton, NJ.[9] "Product Information. Zanosar (streptozocin)." Pharmacia and Upjohn, Kalamazoo, MI.', 1767369485);
